# Simple commands
*   rewrite a commit message

    ~~~ {.bash}
git commit --amend
    ~~~

* show the working tree status

    ~~~ {.bash}
git status
    ~~~

* add tag

    ~~~ {.bash}
git tag -a v1.0
    ~~~

* checkout a dir

    ~~~ {.bash}
git checkout old-kernel -- ./
    ~~~

